Products Page




Additives Page

Product Entry : Only useful while adding additives for a specific product.
Add new: Adds a new additive in the product
Done: Submits the all information inserted for the product in the database (ie. all additives given)
Display Button: All additives in the database are displayed when all entry boxes are empty
                If the additive name is given, its classification information are displayed
Clear Button: Empties all entry boxes

